Date: Sat, 25 Apr 2026 10:43:54 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?perf(workers):=20Step=205b=20=E2=80=94=20bulk?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20product/alias=20resolution?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

find_or_create_product item basi 1-4 RTT yapiyordu (alias SELECT,
products SELECT, INSERT, alias UPSERT). 5528 item'lik sweep'te bu
~55dk ediyor. BulkProductResolver bu adimlarin her birini per-batch
(50 item) tek POST/GET'e indirir:

  1. SELECT product_aliases WHERE alias=in.(...) AND source=eq.X
  2. SELECT products       WHERE canonical_name=in.(...)   (eksikler)
  3. INSERT products       (canonical_name'i hala olmayan kalan)
  4. UPSERT product_aliases (eksik alias'lari product_id'ye bagla)

Beklenti: 5528 / 50 = ~110 batch x 4 RTT = ~440 RTT (~3dk).
Bu Step 5a (BulkWriter — prices/campaigns) ile birlestiginde sweep
suresi 86dk -> ~12-30dk hedefine yaklasir.

Hata durumunda graceful fallback: bulk operasyonlar herhangi bir
noktada exception firlatirsa, batch'in items'lari tek tek
find_or_create_product ile cozulur. Item kacirilmaz.

Entegrasyon:
- core.py: BulkProductResolver + _build_in_filter / _postgrest_in_value
  yardimcilari. find_or_create_product korundu (fallback path'i icin).
- run_worker.py: items 50'lik chunk'larda dolaniyor, her chunk icin
  resolver.resolve_batch + insert_price/campaign loop.
- run_marketfiyati.py: per-market 'pending' buffer; 50 dolunca veya
  sweep sonu _flush_pending tetiklenir.
- _test_bulk_resolver.py: mock client ile 5 vaka (bos, all-new,
  all-existing-alias, mixed, dup-canonical-in-batch) — hepsi gecti.
